Not entirely related to the rest of this PR, but I think this is symptomatic of a very annoying diamond in `DecidableEq (Fin _)` that I've also experienced :(

Not really, it's more the definition of multilinear maps, which don't assume `DecidableEq` but instead quantify over all such instances in the fields `map_add'` and `map_smul'`. So, on a concrete type with a concrete `DecidableEq` instance, you always have to make this small dance when proving that something is multilinear.
